        <h2>
            图解世界战争战法/近代早期的书评 · · · · · ·
            <span class="pl">(<a href="reviews">全部 1 条</a>)</span>
        </h2>
    </header>


        


<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="4577103">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/4577103/" class="title-link">糟糕的翻译毁了这套本来不错的书</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-4577103"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/2853275/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2853275-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2853275/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">haolihaiya</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar20 main-title-rating" title="较差"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-01-12"
      class="main-meta">2011-01-12 13:14:41</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_4577103_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  书本身还是很不错的，内容丰富，配图也能看出是用了心的，更重要的是国内介绍这方面内容的书籍非常有限。可惜翻译的非常糟糕，很多地方前言不答后语，语句都不通顺。比如开篇的几页中不断提到了“帝国”，到底是哪个“帝国”？根据上下文推断在知道这个“帝国”指的是神圣罗马...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/4577103/#comments">(1回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_4577103_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_4577103_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










            <p class="pl" align="right">
                &gt;
